text: Nartovsky () is a rural locality (a settlement) in Yaksatovsky Selsoviet, Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 424 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located on the Kizan River. == References == Category:Rural localities in Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Nartovsky
